@startuml
title Data Views and Export Paths

rectangle "EventStore" as Store
rectangle "List View" as ListView
rectangle "Inspector View" as Inspector
rectangle "Analytics View" as Analytics
rectangle "Timeline View" as Timeline
rectangle "EXPLAIN View" as Explain
rectangle "StdoutEventSink" as Stdout
rectangle "FileEventSink\n(JSONL/JSON)" as FileSink
rectangle "SummaryReportSink\n(JSON/Markdown)" as ReportSink
rectangle "Response Export\n(selected event JSON)" as RespExport

Store --> ListView : event snapshots
Store --> Inspector : selected event/transaction details
Store --> Analytics : grouped metrics by normalized query
Store --> Timeline : query/transaction timeline rows
Inspector --> Explain : selected query + args
Store --> Stdout : headless stream output
Store --> FileSink : persisted raw events
Store --> ReportSink : aggregated slow/N+1/error report
Inspector --> RespExport : export selected response payload

@enduml
